{"title": "Little Miss Grouch", "description": "A young man, known to readers first as the Tyro, meets a young woman all in tears, who is running away on a ship to England from her family and fianc\u00e9. She looks terrible in that state, and is intent on crying through the entire voyage. After she recovers, and turns out to be surpassingly beautiful, he doesn't recognize her. Then she turns her mind to revenge for that failure, and a mixture of hilarity and misery ensues through the entire voyage. - Summary by Mokurai", "duration": 12242, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "2271", "name": "Samuel Hopkins Adams"}], "coverArt": null, "copyright_year": "1915", "genres": ["Romance"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Mokurai"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Mokurai"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Christine Rottger"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Christine Rottger"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "First day out", "readers": [20403], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/littlemissgrouch_2603_librivox/littlemissgrouch_01_adams_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1728}, {"section": 2, "title": "Second day out", "readers": [20403], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/littlemissgrouch_2603_librivox/littlemissgrouch_02_adams_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1642}, {"section": 3, "title": "Third day out", "readers": [20403], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/littlemissgrouch_2603_librivox/littlemissgrouch_03_adams_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1778}, {"section": 4, "title": "Fourth day out", "readers": [20403], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/littlemissgrouch_2603_librivox/littlemissgrouch_04_adams_64kb.mp3", "duration": 848}, {"section": 5, "title": "Fifth day out", "readers": [20403], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/littlemissgrouch_2603_librivox/littlemissgrouch_05_adams_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1451}, {"section": 6, "title": "Sixth day out", "readers": [20403], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/littlemissgrouc